content.text:
Goal: Create a family group linking parents and students.
Data Requirements: Requires id, parents[], students[].
Auth/Security: Only admin/staff can create.
Example Request: POST /family { "id": "fam124", "parents": ["p3"], "students": ["s4","s5"] }
Example Response: { "id": "fam124", "parents": ["p3"], "students": ["s4","s5"] }

Goal: Update parents/students in a family group.
Data Requirements: Path param id; body with updated parents[]/students[].
Auth/Security: Only admin/staff can update.
Example Request: PATCH /family/fam123 { "parents": ["p1","p2","p9"], "students": ["s1","s2"] }
Example Response: { "id": "fam123", "parents": ["p1","p2","p9"], "students": ["s1","s2"] }
